Revision history for Perl extension POE::Component::Log4perl.

0.01  Mon Sep 24 14:01:29 2007
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-AXc -n POE::Component::Log4perl

0.02  17-Sep-2008 K.Esteb
      Updated the Makefile.PL to include POE and Log::Log4perl as
      dependenices.
      Bumped the version number.
      Added some further tests to make sure the basic are working OK.

0.03  03-Oct-2009 K.Esteb
      Added a patch from Adam Flott to add a "trace" level that is now
      supported by Log4perl.

